    @Alias(value="AVRO_FIXED_SCHEMA")
public class FixedSchemaKafkaAvroExtractor
extends KafkaAvroExtractor<Void>
    Extract avro records from a Kafka topic using a fixed schema provided by STATIC_SCHEMA_ROOT_KEY.
